---
title: "Sequence Diagram: Camera Management Service"
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    actor CamDevice as Camera Device
    participant FE  as Frontend<br/>(React/Ionic)
    participant CS  as CameraService<br/>(port 8002)
    participant JWT as JWTHandler<br/>(Infra/Security)
    participant DB  as PostgreSQL

    Note over User,DB: ── CREATE CAMERA ──────────────────────────────────────

    User ->> FE  : Fill camera form<br/>{name, stream_url, protocol, type, location}
    activate FE
    FE   ->> CS  : POST /api/v1/cameras<br/>Authorization: Bearer <token>
    activate CS
    CS   ->> JWT : verify_token(token, "access")
    activate JWT

    alt Token invalid or expired
        JWT -->> CS  : raise JWTDecodeError
        deactivate JWT
        CS  -->> FE  : 401 Unauthorized
        FE  -->> User : Redirect to login
    else Token valid
        JWT -->> CS  : { user_id, email }
        deactivate JWT
        CS   ->> DB  : INSERT INTO cameras<br/>(owner_user_id, name, stream_url,<br/>protocol, status=OFFLINE, is_active=True)
        activate DB
        DB  -->> CS  : { id, created_at }
        deactivate DB
        CS  -->> FE  : 201 Created { camera_id, name, status }
        FE  -->> User : Camera added to dashboard
    end

    Note over User,DB: ── LIST CAMERAS ───────────────────────────────────────

    User ->> FE  : Open cameras dashboard
    FE   ->> CS  : GET /api/v1/cameras<br/>Authorization: Bearer <token>
    CS   ->> JWT : verify_token(token, "access")
    activate JWT
    JWT -->> CS  : { user_id }
    deactivate JWT
    CS   ->> DB  : SELECT * FROM cameras<br/>WHERE owner_user_id = ? ORDER BY created_at DESC
    activate DB
    DB  -->> CS  : [ Camera records ]
    deactivate DB
    CS  -->> FE  : 200 [{ id, name, status, last_heartbeat, location }]
    deactivate CS
    FE  -->> User : Render camera grid with status badges
    deactivate FE

    Note over CamDevice,DB: ── HEARTBEAT (periodic, every N seconds) ─────────────

    CamDevice ->> CS  : POST /api/v1/cameras/{id}/heartbeat<br/>{ latency_ms, frame_drop_rate, uptime_percentage }
    activate CS
    CS   ->> DB  : SELECT * FROM cameras WHERE id = ?
    activate DB
    DB  -->> CS  : Camera record
    deactivate DB
    CS   ->> DB  : UPDATE cameras<br/>SET status='ONLINE', last_heartbeat=NOW()
    activate DB
    DB  -->> CS  : OK
    deactivate DB
    CS   ->> DB  : INSERT INTO camera_health<br/>(camera_id, latency_ms,<br/>frame_drop_rate, uptime_percentage)
    activate DB
    DB  -->> CS  : { id, recorded_at }
    deactivate DB
    CS  -->> CamDevice : 200 { status: "ONLINE", recorded_at }
    deactivate CS

    Note over User,DB: ── DELETE CAMERA ──────────────────────────────────────

    User ->> FE  : Click "Delete Camera" → Confirm dialog
    activate FE
    FE   ->> CS  : DELETE /api/v1/cameras/{id}<br/>Authorization: Bearer <token>
    activate CS
    CS   ->> JWT : verify_token(token, "access")
    activate JWT
    JWT -->> CS  : { user_id }
    deactivate JWT
    CS   ->> DB  : SELECT * FROM cameras WHERE id = ?
    activate DB
    DB  -->> CS  : Camera record
    deactivate DB

    alt user_id ≠ owner_user_id
        CS  -->> FE  : 403 Forbidden
        FE  -->> User : Show error
    else Authorized
        CS   ->> DB  : DELETE FROM cameras WHERE id = ?
        activate DB
        DB  -->> CS  : OK
        deactivate DB
        CS  -->> FE  : 204 No Content
        FE  -->> User : Remove camera from list
    end
    deactivate CS
    deactivate FE
